Update: Wiki
Update: man pages
Add: cmd slacker pin / unpin — permanent "positive" pin (the opposite of freeze)
- Save INSIDE the blacklist with @repo 100% pkgname syntax (no new files).
- Commands: pin repo:package and unpin package (unpin with no argument = list).
- Semantics: a pinned package is derived ONLY from the pinned repo, ignoring
priority, in ALL commands (incl. upgrade-all). A package has at most one
pin (re-pin = replace). thanks to my dear friend and real life neighbor @gcosbug ;)
